{"tid":245160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(音響JJ) 想換amp，求推介","createTime":"2017-05-16T04:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T06:15:01.000Z","uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"262495d9f70469be5b112302d952e4ba84645b17","tid":245160,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:26:04.000Z","msg":"依家用緊Micromega AI180，喇叭用B&amp;W CM5 S2，CDP就用Cambridge CD10。本時鍾音聽人聲，高音勁，聲底夠厚，音場夠闊，同樂器分析度較高。其實一路都覺得唔錯。但之前聽過Moon Neo 340i之後，畀佢個音場同通透感染咗。但上網睇完之後，發覺Audia Flight 3S都好似幾正。依家有有幾個選擇<br />\n<br />\nMoon Neo 340i<br />\nAudia Flight 3S<br />\nLuxman L-590AX II<br />\n<br />\n但好怕換完冇咩分別，定要用到金仔E-470先有明顯改變呢？求全能連登仔推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e026929f7936d544d12133d500e80f83aaceecb0","tid":245160,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}